      "post_content": "Coming to a city near you Dec 2012 ;-P  \n  \n~\"Dr. Peter Venkman: This city is headed for a disaster of biblical proportions.  \nMayor: What do you mean, \"biblical\"?  \nDr Ray Stantz: What he means is Old Testament, Mr. Mayor, real [wrath of God](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=wrath of God) type stuff.  \nDr. Peter Venkman: Exactly.  \nDr Ray Stantz: Fire and brimstone coming down from the skies! Rivers and seas boiling!  \nDr. Egon Spengler: Forty years of darkness! [Earthquake](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Earthquake)s, volcanoes...  \nWinston Zeddemore: The dead rising from the grave!  \nDr. Peter Venkman: Human sacrifice, dogs and cats living together... [mass hysteria](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=mass hysteria)! \"",
